ttp_template:
<group name="memory_total_memory_used_memory_free">
Processor Pool Total: {{MEMORY_TOTAL}} Used: {{MEMORY_USED}} Free: {{MEMORY_FREE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>

textfsm_parsed.PROCESS: *Init*, IOSD ipc task, *Dead*, EEM ED Syslog, Chunk Manager, EEM Server, CWAN OIR Handler, *MallocLite*, RF Slave Main Th, EEM ED Generic, Crypto IKEv2, MRIB Process, Pool Manager

textfsm_template:
Value MEMORY_TOTAL (\d+)
Value MEMORY_USED (\d+)
Value MEMORY_FREE (\d+)
Value List PROCESS_ID (\d+)
Value List PROCESS_ALLOCATED (\d+)
Value List PROCESS_FREED (\d+)
Value List PROCESS_HOLDING (\d+)
Value List PROCESS (.+?)

Start
  ^Processor\s+Pool\s+Total:\s+${MEMORY_TOTAL}\s+Used:\s+${MEMORY_USED}\s+Free:\s+${MEMORY_FREE}
  ^\s*lsmpi_io\s+Pool
  ^\s*PID\s+TTY\s+Allocated\s+Freed\s+Holding\s+Getbufs\s+Retbufs\s+Process\s*$$ -> Process
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error

Process
  ^\s*${PROCESS_ID}\s+\d+\s+${PROCESS_ALLOCATED}\s+${PROCESS_FREED}\s+${PROCESS_HOLDING}\s+\d+\s+\d+\s+${PROCESS}\s*$$
  ^\s*\d+\s+Total\s*$$
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
